<title>白宫顾问谈美股暴跌：挺住，不卖就不赔！</title>
<link>http://weixin.sogou.com/weixin?type=2&amp;query=%E7%8E%AF%E7%90%83%E6%97%B6%E6%8A%A5+%E7%99%BD%E5%AE%AB%E9%A1%BE%E9%97%AE%E8%B0%88%E7%BE%8E%E8%82%A1%E6%9A%B4%E8%B7%8C%EF%BC%9A%E6%8C%BA%E4%BD%8F%EF%BC%8C%E4%B8%8D%E5%8D%96%E5%B0%B1%E4%B8%8D%E8%B5%94%EF%BC%81</link>
